Package net.objectzoo.delegates.adapters

This package contains support classes that can be used to wrap standard delegates to be asynchronous.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Action0ToAction0Async
    An adapter that converts a conventional Action0 to an Action0Async.
    Action0ToAsyncAction0
    An adapter that converts an Action0 to a new Action0, that makes an asynchronous calls to the original Action0 upon invocation.
    Action2ToAction2Async<T1,T2>
    An adapter that converts a conventional Action2 or BiConsumer to an Action2Async.
    Action2ToAsyncAction2<T1,T2>
    An adapter that converts an Action2 or BiConsumer to a new Action2, that makes an asynchronous calls to the original Action0 upon invocation.
    Action3ToAction3Async<T1,T2,T3>
    An adapter that converts a conventional Action3 to an Action3Async.
    Action3ToAsyncAction3<T1,T2,T3>
    An adapter that converts an Action3 to a new Action3, that makes an asynchronous calls to the original Action0 upon invocation.
    Action4ToAction4Async<T1,T2,T3,T4>
    An adapter that converts a conventional Action4 to an Action4Async.
    Action4ToAsyncAction4<T1,T2,T3,T4>
    An adapter that converts an Action4 to a new Action4, that makes an asynchronous calls to the original Action0 upon invocation.
    ActionToActionAsync<T>
    An adapter that converts a conventional Action or Consumer to an ActionAsync.
    ActionToAsyncAction<T>
    An adapter that converts an Action or Consumer to a new Action, that makes an asynchronous calls to the original Action0 upon invocation.
    Function0ToFunction0Async<R>
    An adapter that converts a conventional Function0 or Supplier to an Function0Async.
    Function2ToFunction2Async<T1,T2,R>
    An adapter that converts a conventional Function2 or BiFunction to an Function2Async.
    Function3ToFunction3Async<T1,T2,T3,R>
    An adapter that converts a conventional Function3 to an Function3Async.
    Function4ToFunction4Async<T1,T2,T3,T4,R>
    An adapter that converts a conventional Function4 to an Function4Async.
    FunctionToFunctionAsync<T,R>
    An adapter that converts a conventional Function to an FunctionAsync.

Package net.objectzoo.delegates.adapters Description

This package contains support classes that can be used to wrap standard delegates to be asynchronous.
